SUBSTITUTE FOR
HOUSE BILL NO. 5813
A bill to amend 1939 PA 280, entitled
"The social welfare act,"
(MCL 400.1 to 400.119b) by adding section 106c.
THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF MICHIGAN ENACT:
1 Sec. 106c. (1) Beginning October 1, 2026, the department shall
2 annually report the medical assistance error rate and improper
3 payment rate on the department's website and to the standing
4 committees of the house of representatives and senate on oversight.
5 (2) As used in this section:
6 (a) "Error rate" means the total of all of the following:
7 (i) Payments under this state's plan with respect to ineligible
8 individuals and families.
9 (ii) Overpayments on behalf of eligible individuals and
